The Eau de Parfum is made from the finest of ingredients chosen and mixed with a fine balance that has been mastered by the perfumer. He is a man who has exemplary tastes and the need to own the most exquisite and beautiful creations that add to his aura of success. Opening notes of luscious blackcurrant, citrusy lemon and bergamot comes as a blast of freshness on a dull, cloudy day. The heart hides accords of jasmine, violet, patchouli and crispy apple. Cedar, musk and rosewood bring up the rear and leave a trail of sensuous subtlety. The scent of Raymond 11.4µ that creates an aura of magnetism around you. The strong, smooth lines of his aquiline jaw lend inspiration to the bold lines of the flacon that contains the smooth redolence of Raymond 11.4µ. The metal stopper add a touch of finesse to overall look of the fragrance. Splash around in the pond of rejuvenation that is 11.4µ and be the man who leaves such an impact that nobody ever forgets him.

Title: Roberto Cavalli Eau De Parfum - 50 ml(For Women)
Police Dark EDT  -  100 ml(For Men)
Description: He is sure to attract more than few glances as he walks confidently and slides into his jet-black luxury car. As he zooms off in style, a trail of his masculine aura leaves his onlookers spellbound. The mass premium fragrance of Police Dark EDT blends with this blazing trail for a lasting memory. Olfactory Family: Aromati-woody-oriental-citrusy The unexpected combination of aromatic, woody, oriental and citrus accords, this fragrance complements the man who knows how to play it. Refined and Mysterious A mixture of invigorating aromas, this fragrance portrays the ruthless heart that is refined and mysterious. Perfect for Evening and Night This eau de toilette is perfect to complement his ensembles on those special evenings or party nights.  Strong, Spicy and Long-lasting Fragrance The Dark EDT enwraps him in a fragrance that is strong, spicy and long lasting.

Title: Mary Quant HAVOC GOLD EDT  -  75 ml(For Men)
Description: Excellent Perfum To Make Your Body Fresh & Germless. Cologne Spray With Long Time Stay Smell. Havoc is classified as a gorgeous powdery mossy, green, aldehydic chypre with a floral that begins with a tantalizing floral creme broule. It gradually settles down to a really lovely retro mix of green floracy and a faint musk. It is a very rare and hard to find perfume. This Fragrance was originally produced back in the 1970'S by MARY QUANT. Havoc Gold, a bottle of 75 ml. with a tempting smell.

Title: Brut Passion Aftershave  -  100 ml(For Men)
Description: Brut Passion is an aftershave for the man who loves his fragrances wild and powerful. A generous treat to your nose, the Brut Passion aftershave is an ultimate masculine fragrance that refreshes and soothes with an invigorating charm. Intense with an assortment of bright and soulful aromas, this aftershave concoction provides a cooling sensation to your skin after a shave and gives you that breezy relief that keeps you refreshed throughout the day. With great longevity, the Brut Passion Mass Premium aftershave lotion enthralls and energizes with its passionate intensity and stands out as a perfect expression of virile charm and seduction.

Title: Armaf Skin Couture Eau de Parfum  -  100 ml(For Girls)

Choose from a selection of modern, invigorating and inspiring scents for stylish and sophisticated men and a selection of glamorous, indulgent and irresistible unique designer fragrances for women.

Title: Avon Little Gold Dress Eau de Parfum  -  50 ml(For Girls)

Title: Calvin Klein Euphoria W Eau de Parfum  -  100 ml(For Women)
Description: Provocative, Sexy, Sensual. Experience the mystery of EUPHORIA, an addictive oriental with contrasting exotic fruits, seductive florals and a rich creamy signature.

Title: David Beckham Signature EDT  -  75 ml(For Men)
Description: Designer suit, loosened tie, leather oxfords, carefully careless hair, a casual stroll by the breezy Thames with a beautiful woman and Beckham Signature Man - bliss. The Signature Man is an impression of subtle sensuality, a compelling enigma. Suave and confident, he has a refreshing world view and appreciates the finer things in life. No rose-tinted glasses for him; he sees the world as it is and yet appreciates all that life offers to him. For him, the Signature Man Eau de Toilette is more than just a fragrance - it's an expression of his charismatic personality. Developed by perfumer Beatrice Piquet, Beckham Signature Man compels with its woody oriental scent. This woody oriental luxury perfume opens with a fresh top note of mandarin and watermelon, only to trail into a heart of lantana, warm cypress and juniper. The invigorating base note, comprising of moss, white amber and patchouli, is emblematic of a personality that is refined yet compelling. The Signature Man has a youthful zest, a lust for life - something that is perfectly symbolized by the designer bottle that has been inspired by modern architecture. With Beckham Signature Man make a statement, tell the world who you really are.

Title: Brickell Revitalizing Anti-Aging Cream
Description: If used twice daily as instructed, this jar will last approximately 45 days.Significantly diminish wrinkles, lines, crow's feet, and signs of aging with the best anti-aging cream for men. Our powerful, clinically proven men's anti aging cream is formulated for men's thicker skin to remove even the deepest wrinkles and lines.What It Does: Our All Natural Anti-Aging Cream for men uses an exclusive mixture of powerful, natural ingredients to penetrate into the skin to firm, smooth, and tighten. Fine lines will become noticeably less visible almost immediately, while wrinkles and other signs of aging will be dramatically reduced over time.How It Works: DMAE (Dimethylethanolamine): A powerful natural ingredient that helps the underlying face muscles to contract, thus tightening the skin. The skin is most affected by the atrophy of facial muscles underneath it, so it prevents the folding (wrinkles) of the skin.MSM (Methylsulfonylmethane): A nutrient found in most well known super foods (spinach, kale) which reduces age spots and eventual skin pigmentation issues some parts of the face get over time.Hyaluronic Acid: This gel-like water holding molecule retains over 1,000 times its weight in water, thus making it the ultimate moisturizer. Wrinkles are often caused by sun exposure and natural dehydration of the skin as we age. So by flooding our cells with hydration from hyaluronic acid, we can reduce lines and prevent future wrinkles.These ingredients, along with other powerful, natural ingredients have been scientifically formulated together to create the best anti aging cream for men.

Title: NOVA BIOS POMEGRANATE POWDER
Description: It fights acne, pimples and rashesBecause of its healing properties, pomegranate peels can effectively fight acne, pimples and rashes. Allow them to cool and grind them in a grinder or mixer. Make a paste of this powder with lemon juice or rose water and apply it all over your face, especially on your pimples or acne. Let it dry for a while then wash it off thoroughly with lukewarm water.It prevents wrinkles and other signs of ageing.The peels prevents breakdown of collagen in your skin, in turn promoting cell growth, which helps delay signs of ageing and wrinkles effectivelyHow to use it: Take two spoonfuls of sun-dried and powdered peel and add little milk to it. If you have oily skin, add rose water to the powder instead of milk and make a paste out of it. Apply this paste on your face and keep it till it dries. Wash your face with lukewarm water and try using the powder at least twice a week for better results.3 It acts as a natural moisturiser.Pomegranate peels are great for your skin. It hydrates and protects your skin from pollutants and other environmental toxins. It restores the pH balance of the skin. The ellagic acid present in the peels lock moisture in the skin. keeping it soft and supple.How to use it: Grind sun-dried pomegranate peels in a mixer and empty the powder into a clean bowl. Make sufficient powder to last you for a week and store it in an airtight container. Take two spoonfuls of the powder and mix well with some yoghurt to make a paste out of it. Description: Retinol 4%Retinol is a whitening agent and mild peeling at conc of 4%Chemical Peels are acids therefore should be used under the Supervision of trained cosmetologists.Always do Patch Test when using the peel for the first time.Patch test: Apply small amount of peel below neck or armpit, see for any redness beyond the margin of application, if seendiscontinue the procedure. If no redness or itching continue with the procedureProcedure:Cleanse the skin with oil free cleanser, if using oil containing cleanser, after cleansing whip with alcohol or spirit. oil blocks the acid therefore desired action is not achieved.Apply Peel with brush or ear Buds, gel peels can be best applied with gloved fingers. start applying from the forehead upto the neck, application time should not be more than 20 seconds. keep peel for 2-8 hrs depending on your skin habituality of peeling and the peel strength. Spray neutralizer, keep for 1 min.wash with water., apply sunscreen and good moisturiser for 7 days twice daily.Post Peel:Success of the peeling depends on sunprotection and moisturisingfirst the skin dies so becomes black don't worry this is the skin that is going to peel of itselfThere are two types of peeling microscopic that is not seen by naked eyes, and macroscopic peeling that is visualised very wellDo not remove the skin by your self.Don't use soap for 2-3 days, thereafter, use mild soap for 7-8 days, don't scrub too hardNote: If you don't get desired results doesnt mean the peel is not working it only means that your skin is tough for the peel you are using. then its time to use stronger peels or increase the application time of the peel in the next sitting.

The pieces consists of a black zinc-copper alloy with intricate inlays of pure silver. Bidriware is made by traditional methods including casting, chiseling and manual polishing. Materials such as earth from the Bidar Fort, castor oil, resin, copper sulphate and ammonium chloride are used to create these works of art that are like no other.All our products are genuine and made by master artisans in Bidar.
